OL,5, A support scheme set up for Church of  
OL,6, England abuse survivors risks          
OL,7, re-traumatising victims, a report seen 
OL,8, by the BBC has concluded.              
OL,10,FOne man's dealings with the scheme left
OL,11,Fhim suicidal, says the report by the   
OL,12,FChurch's Independent Safeguarding Board
OL,13,F(ISB).                                 
